No. D-2873. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 29, 2016.

In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Paul Michael KAUFMAN.

Paul Michael Kaufman, of Cleveland, Ohio, is suspended from the practice of law *1255in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
